==Badge==
==Possible specialist Arctic sovereignty role==
It has been suggested in a Canadian professional military journal that the regiment&#x27;s third battalion (3 RCR) could be adapted to become a specialized light infantry battalion that is able to deploy parachute infantry and marine infantry company groups to support the protection of Canada&#x27;s sovereignty in the Arctic.

